text: The following lists events that happened in 1994 in Iceland. ==Incumbents== *President - Vigdís Finnbogadóttir *Prime Minister - Davíð Oddsson ==Events== ==Births== Martin Hermannsson *3 January - Einar Kristgeirsson, alpine skier. *3 January - Gudmunda Brynja Óladóttir, footballer *27 January - Erla Ásgeirsdóttir, alpine skier. *9 May - Árni Vilhjálmsson, footballer *16 September - Martin Hermannsson, basketball player *3 November - Tinna Odinsdottir, artistic gymnast *10 November - Aron Elís Þrándarson, footballer ===Full date missing=== *Freydis-Halla Einarsdóttir, alpine skier ==Deaths== *7 April - Albert Guðmundsson, footballer (b. 1923) *18 November - Lúdvik Jósepsson, politician (b. 1914) ==References== Category:1990s in Iceland Iceland Iceland Category:Years of the 20th century in Iceland
title: 1994 in Iceland
